title: Imm Aim Vegetarian and Bike Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Thai, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Serving vegetarian food using mostly organic produce from local producers. Thai food, salads, pasta, smoothies, fruit drinks, and coffee. Located down the street from YMCA on Santitham Road between the YMCA and the round-about. Kitchen closed at 8pm. Previously named Pun Pun.
